# Project Conventions

- Package manager: **pnpm** (never use npm or yarn)
- When suggesting or running install/run commands, always use `pnpm` (e.g. `pnpm install`, `pnpm run dev`, `pnpm dlx`)
- Supabase: **remote instance** (use `pnpm supabase db push` for migrations, not local reset)
